title: NFL Week 16 Sunday Recap; Eagles finally emerge past Cowboys in NFC East? (Football 12/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 16 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Cowboys-Eagles (4:00), Saints-Titans (27:00), Steelers-Jets (39:15), Raiders-Chargers (44:30), Chiefs-Bears (52:00), Ravens-Browns (1:03:30), Seahawks-Cardinals (1:12:45), Bengals-Dolphins (1:23:30), Giants-Redskins (1:31:15), Lions-Broncos (1:35:00), Jags-Falcons (1:37:45) and Panthers-Colts (1:41:00).
